                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "2e8da527baf7489f9bd0e",
                    "stepText": "Excellent. Next, use the calculated exponent from step 3 to evaluate the decay factor, which is given by $!$e^{-\\lambda t}$!$. What is the numerical value of this decay factor?",
